    <div id="dc-parkbody">
	    <div id="dc-parkgenericmaincontentbody" class="BodyContent1">
			<p class=header>State Parks' Vehicle Registrations Program</p>
<p align=left><img alt="" style="width:166px;height:83px" border=0 align=right src="/SiteCollectionImages/parks/Programs/OHVridingatAHRA.jpg">Colorado State Parks administers the state's vehicle registrations programs for boats, off-highway vehicles (OHVs) and snowmobiles.  Please click on the program name below for more information.<br>
 <br>
<a href="/Boating/Registrations">Boating Program: Boat Registration information</a><br>
 <br>
<a href="/OHVsandSnowmobiles/OHVProgram/OHVRegistrations">OHV Program: OHV registrations, including ATVs, dirtbikes, motorbikes, and other off-highway vehicles</a><br>
 <br>
<a href="/OHVsandSnowmobiles/SnowmobileProgram/Registrations">Snowmobile Program: Snowmobile Registration Information</a><br>
<br>
For more information, please call or write the Registration Unit:<br>
Office hours are Monday thru Friday, 8am-5pm (excluding holidays).<br>
13787 S. Hwy 85<br>
Littleton, CO 80125<br>
303-791-1920 - Office<br>
303-470-0782 - Fax<br>
<a href="mailto:dnr.ivrsparks@state.co.us">dnr.ivrsparks@state.co.us</a><br>
<br>
<span class=header2>Registration Application (submit by mail only)<br>
</span><a href="/SiteCollectionImages/parks/Programs/BoatingProgram/SystemWideFormsandInfo/RegForm11-09.pdf" target="_blank">Boat, OHV, and Snowmobile Registration Application</a><br>
<br>
<span class=header2>Renew your Registration Online<br>
<br>
</span><em>** Due to a printing error, the PIN on the OHV renewal cards are incorrect.  Please use the link that is provided for customers who do not have their renewal cards to use your registration number, last name, and date of birth to look up the registration.  We apologize for any inconvenience. **<br>
</em><br>
    <a href="https://ivrs.parks.state.co.us/" target="_blank"><img width=271 height=55 alt="" style="width:161px;height:55px" src="/SiteCollectionImages/parks/Programs/Registrations/RegistrationButton-2.JPG"></a></p>

		</div><!-- end parkmaincontentbody -->
